original_title: The Best of Insomniac with Dave Attell Volume 2
overview: Dave Attell's video travelogue of after-hour experiences around the globe. Attell sets out to explore the nightlife in Las Vegas, Amsterdam, Key West, Miami, Boise, Kansas City, Anchorage, New York City, Charleston, WV and Austin. Includes never-before-seen uncensored footage of scenes too racy for even Comedy Central to show.
title: The Best of Insomniac with Dave Attell Volume 2
